(33, 'Privacy Policy', 'what-is-uncategorised-article', '', '<h3 style="color: #be1010; font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, verdana, times, tahoma; margin-top: 2px; margin-bottom: 2px; margin-left: 10px; font-weight: normal;">Privacy Policy</h3>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:12.0pt; margin-left:.5in;line-height:normal"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black"> </span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">GiftsJaipur.com</span></strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA"> is committed to <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">safeguarding your privacy online</span></strong>. We recognize your need for reasonable control of personally identifiable information that you share with GiftsJaipur.com. <br /> <br /> When you order, we need to know your name, e-mail address, mailing address, credit card number, and expiration date. This allows us to process and fulfill your order. This will used only for the service you have sought and would not be under any circumstances passed on to any other commercial purpose. GiftsJaipur.com will not disclose any of your personally identifiable information except when we have your permission or under special circumstances, such as when we believe in good faith that the law requires it. <br /> <br /> Although we track the total number of visitors to each of sites in an aggregate form to allow us to update an improve our sites, personally identifiable information is not extracted in this process. Any cookie technology (where our servers deposit special codes on a visitor''s computer) will only be used to track non-personal information such as type of browser, operating system, and domain names to improve our visitor''s online experience. <br /> <br /> </span><strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#CE0000;mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">How does GiftsJaipur.com protect customer information?</span></strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"> <br /> <br /> When you place orders it is through a secure server. The secure server software (SSL) encrypts all information you input including your credit card number, before it is sent to us. This makes it unreadable as it travels across the Internet. Furthermore, all of the customer data we collect is protected against unauthorized access. <br /> <br /> </span><strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#CE0000;mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">Will GiftsJaipur.com disclose the information it collects to outside parties?</span></strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;; mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US; mso-fareast-language:EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA"> <br /> <br /> <strong>GiftsJaipur.com</strong> does not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to others. By using our web site, you consent to the collection and use of this information by GiftsJaipur.com. If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page so that you are always aware of what information we collect, how we use it, and under what circumstances we disclose it.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 31, '2008-08-11 15:14:11', 62, '', '2012-06-20 14:32:59', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2006-10-10 12:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 11, 0, 4, 'Gift Delivery At Jaipur, gifts flowers, flower gifts, deliver gift, sending gifts, online flower shops, gifts and delivery, flower send, flowers to delivery, florists delivery, floral deliveries, flower store, bouquet delivery, gifts to deliver, fruit gift baskets, flowers and delivery, flower deliveries, gift flowers, send flowers to, baskets, flowers gift, send gift, flower bouquet, flowers delivery, mothers day gifts, gift send, florist flower delivery, flowers send, flower online, flowers deliver, deliver flower, send flower, delivery for flowers, flowers shop, birthday cakes, flowers by delivery, on line flowers, delivery flower, flowers shops, deliver flowers, online flower, flowers to send, flower bouquets, fruit basket, flower deliver, send a gift, gifts to send, wedding flowers, florist, floral delivery, flowers to deliver, delivery of flowers, delivery flowers, florists, flower shop, flower shops, sending flowers, flowers for delivery, flowers on line, send flowers, flower delivery, gifts for delivery, gifts delivery, gift delivery', '', 0, 934, 'html_title=\nmeta_description=\nmeta_keywords=Gift Delivery At Jaipur, gifts flowers, flower gifts, deliver gift, sending gifts, online flower shops, gifts and delivery, flower send, flowers to delivery, florists delivery, floral 