(35, 'Delivery policy', 'Delivery-Policy', '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: ''Bell MT'', serif, font-size: 13pt; line-height: 150%;">Gift Jaipur is a reliable and registered company. While doing business, we are completely committed to customer satisfaction and indulge only in ethical and healthy business practices. Assured of quality, we offer and deliver the best at the best prices.<br /> •	We are extremely particular about ‘on time delivery’. However, they may be a delay because of unforeseen circumstances like rain, traffic, etc. <br /> •	In unavoidable circumstances, the delay in delivery of gift may vary between +/- 30 minutes.<br /> •	All charges mentioned are inclusive of delivery charges.<br /> •	There are no extra changes for midnight delivery.<br /> •	We provide a 24 hrs services.<br /> •	For on time delivery, we confirm the availability of the receiver at the mentioned address before the delivery to assure comfortable delivery.<br /> •	 To further understand the address, we may call the receiver on the mentioned number prior to the delivery.<br /> •	In case of delivery at a non specific place like hospital, government office, etc, we may ask the receiver to meet the delivery person at a key point to avoid any hassles.<br /> •	Cakes and other perishable items are custom-made after the order is placed according to your specifications. In case of any unavoidable variation, you shall be duly informed beforehand.<br /> •	The chefs prepare cakes between 8 AM to 8 PM. Please make your order considerably.<br /> •	For delivery in suburbs and surrounding areas of Jaipur like Kukas, Harmada, Sirsi, Gauner, etc, please extend one day’s notice to organize the delivery in the outskirts. <br /> •	Gift Jaipur is here to deliver happiness in the form of gifts and bouquets to your loved ones. Our intentions are right and our practices are ethical. In case of any suggestion, complaint or information, we request you to get in touch with one of our customer care personnel.</span></p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 28, '2008-08-10 23:15:36', 62, '', '2012-09-05 10:22:29', 62, 62, '2012-09-05 10:22:29', '2006-10-10 04:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=1\nlink_titles=0\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=0\nlink_section=0\nshow_category=0\nlink_category=0\nshow_vote=0\nshow_author=0\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 18, 0, 2, 'Gift Delivery At Jaipur, gifts flowers, flower gifts, deliver gift, sending gifts, online flower shops, gifts and delivery, flower send, flowers to delivery, florists delivery, floral deliveries, flower store, bouquet delivery, gifts to deliver, fruit gift baskets, flowers and delivery, flower deliveries, gift flowers, send flowers to, baskets, flowers gift, send gift, flower bouquet, flowers delivery, mothers day gifts, gift send, florist flower delivery, flowers send, flower online, flowers deliver, deliver flower, send flower, delivery for flowers, flowers shop, birthday cakes, flowers by delivery, on line flowers, delivery flower, flowers shops, deliver flowers, online flower, flowers to send, flower bouquets, fruit basket, flower deliver, send a gift, gifts to send, wedding flowers, florist, floral delivery, flowers to deliver, delivery of flowers, delivery flowers, florists, flower shop, flower shops, sending flowers, flowers for delivery, flowers on line, send flowers, flower delivery, gifts for delivery, gifts delivery, gift delivery', '', 0, 842, 'html_title=\nmeta_description=\nmeta_keywords=Gift Delivery At Jaipur, gifts flowers, flower gifts, deliver gift, sending gifts, online flower shops, gifts and delivery, flower send, flowers to delivery, florists delivery, floral deliveries, flower store, bouquet delivery, gifts to deliver, fruit gift baskets, flowers and delivery, flower deliveries, gift flowers, send flowers to, baskets, flowers gift, send gift, flower bouquet, flowers