(36, 'About Us', 'About-Us', '', '<p><span style="font-family: ''Bell MT'', serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;">Gift Jaipur is a single point interface where you can send greetings in the form of gifts, cakes, bouquets, etc to your loved ones in Jaipur from any corner of the world. Registered under the Product of Golygon, the Company has pioneered the idea of sending personalized gifts in a short time span within the city of Jaipur from anywhere in the world.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Bell MT'', serif; font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;"> <strong>Our Network</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: ''Bell MT'', serif; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%;">Gift Jaipur brings together local yet reputed product and service providers of Jaipur in one network. The company enjoys tie-ups with leading names in the industry and their quality products are now being demanded, hosted and delivered at your doorstep. Whatever be the occasion, Gifts Jaipur facilitates quality products being customized and tailor made according to your needs and delivers it to the concerned party in Jaipur, within no time.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-family: ''Bell MT'', serif; font-size: 16pt; line-height: 150%;"> <strong>Our Service</strong></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-family: &quot;Bell MT&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;">There is a dedicated team that manages the logistics and ensures on-time delivery. The ‘on-time delivery’ facet makes Gift Jaipur stand out and helps build an ever increasing pool of satisfied customers. Gift Jaipur assures quality and purity of food products through its distinguished supplier base. All perishables are prepared at reputed food caterers and retailers only after the order is placed. </span></p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 3, 0, 28, '2008-08-10 23:16:20', 62, '', '2012-09-05 08:54:49', 62, 62, '2012-09