(56, 'Birthday Gifts', 'Birthday-Gifts', '', '<table border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">With the trend of online gifting coming into vogue, sending gifts to any part of the world is just a click away. Now, to send gifts you don’t need to go anywhere, no need to spend your precious time in hours of shopping or run around in the whole city for your favorite gift item. You can send various gifts to anyone from your home; choose the best from a wide variety of gifts. Make your shopping a smart shopping.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><img src="images/stories/Birthday celebration.jpg" border="0" width="180" height="140" /><br /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="www.giftjaipur.com"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; color: #009eb8;">"Gift Jaipur”</span></a> is here to help you to surprise your friend and show your love and care towards them. Though “Gift Jaipur” is in its early stages but their delivery service can be compared to any of the existing venture of this field. You can send online gift anywhere in Jaipur from any part of the world. Gift Jaipur provide you variety of cakes, chocolates and flowers which can express best of your emotions. To keep all your excitement preserved, GiftJaipur also provide even in the midnight. It’s completely a new way of celebrating someone’s birthday online. Birthday gift choices available at gift Jaipur are countless.</p>\r\n<table style="text-align: justify;" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://giftjaipur.com/Birthday"><img src="images/stories/Giftjaipur_assorted_birthday_gift_basket.jpg" border="0" width="130" height="120" /></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="http://giftjaipur.com/joomla-home?page=shop.product_details&amp;product_id=108&amp;flypage=flypage.tpl&amp;pop=0"><img src="images/stories/Giftjaipur_bdmug1.jpg" border="0" width="130" height="120" /></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="http://giftjaipur.com/birthday-cakes"><img src="images/stories/Giftja