(57, 'Customize your gift', 'customize-your-gift', '', '<p align="justify">In this section we would like to introduce the biggest advantage of choosing giftjaipur for delivering your gift to your loved ones across Jaipur. Just imagine you have any idea, to make your gift more presentable and impressive. You are sitting far away and want to implement the same idea. You would certainly like to search for a gift delivery service. This was the whole some motive of origination of GiftJaipur. Here at giftJaipur we understand that gift is representation of feelings, emotions. Many a time to express these we choose some different and creative ideas. We are here to help you and play as per your instruction. To understand your emotions behind the gift and implement those creative ideas that will make your emotion to be expressed in the best possible manner.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p align="justify">Check out the creative ideas we have already implemented. We got a very positive feedback from our customers for this particular service. Will be delightful, to repeat any gift idea that you like.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 10, 0, 37, '2012-06-25 18:26:36', 62, '', '2012-07-02 09:36:01', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-06-25 18:26:36', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=1\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=0\nshow_author=0\nshow_create_date=0\nshow_modify_date=0\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 8, 0, 3, '', '', 0, 28, 'html_title=\nmeta_description=\nmeta_keywords=\nrobots=index, follow\ngooglebot=\ncopyright='),
(58, 'Unique chocolate cake and flowers', 'Unique-chocolate-cake-and-flowers', '', '<table border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href="http://giftjaipur.com/Combo-Product?page=shop.product_details&amp;flypage=flypage_images.tpl&amp;product_id=203&amp;category_id=11" title="Product Discription"><img src="images/stories/showcase/24 red rose and chocolate cake giftjaipur.jpg" border="0" /></a></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p align="justify">Personalized gifts allow you to share a message from your heart. Recently a value added customer asked us for designer chocolate cake along with beautiful bouquet of flowers on her husband''s birthday. She wanted everything to be unique. So we provided her with some unique cake and extremely distinguishable flower bunch pictures. She was flattered by the ideas. Along with cakes and flowers we delivered ballons and musical candle that too right at midnight.</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '', 1, 10, 0, 37, '2012-07-02 09:08:13', 62, '', '2012-07-02 09:49:05', 62, 62, '2012-07-02 09:49:06', '2012-07-02 09:08:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 3, 'html_title=\nmeta_description=\nmeta_keywords=\nrobots=index, follow\ngooglebot=\ncopyright='),
(59, 'Cake in design of letter ''A''', 'Cake-in-design-of-letter-A', '', '<p align="justify">Gift Jaipur can deliver a variety of personalized gifts. Once a value added customer wanted to send birthday cake to his girlfriend in a shape of his girlfriend''s initial i.e. ''A''. While making of the cake, Our chef''s were so excited that they put some extra designing and make it a perfect romantic cake. The girl was very much excited after seeing the cake. We got a very delightful feedback and this all makes us feel happy.</p>', '', 1, 10, 0, 37, '2012-07-05 03:35:59', 62, '', '2012-07-05 04:00:00', 62, 62, '2012-07-05 04:00:00', '2012-07-05 03:35:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 2, 0, 1, '', '', 0, 6, 'html_title=\nmeta_description=\nmeta_keywords=\nrobots=index, follow\ngooglebot=\ncopyright='),
(60, 'Shopping for Rakhi', 'Shopping-for-Rakhi', '', '<p style="text-align: justify;">Among various festivals of India, Rakhi is a famous festival that is celebrated with lot of verve and pleasure throughout India. All the siblings gather together to make the celebration splendid. Rakhi festival symbolize the eternal love and affection which holds the brother-sister relationship since ages and has become the true spirit of this relationship.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>Rakhi Gift Ideas for Sisters</strong></span><br /><span style="font-size: 13px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"> Ladies are tend to be more choosy but that doesn''t means that brothers should shell out all their bucks in purchasing gift for their sweet sisters. The value of gift is not decided by the number of zeros added in its cost price but by the affection and sentiments attached to it. Gift Jaipur provide variety of gift items for sisters like <a href="Chocolates">chocolates</a>, <a href="Chocolates">soft toys</a>, various types of <a href="Flowers">flowers</a> and play sweet tunes of the day with our mouthwatering <a href="egg-less-cakes">fresh eggless cakes</a> and in the shape of your sister initial.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">Rakhi Gift Ideas for Brothers</span></strong><br /><span style="font-size: 13px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;"> Going by the choice of your dear brothers, gift them their favourite <a href="Chocolates">chocolates</a> and<a href="Flowers"> bouquet</a>. You can add sweetness to the day with delicious Chocolates, <a href="Sweets">Mithais</a> or <a href="Dry-Fruits">Dry Fruits</a>. Enjoy the eternal bonding with brothers by gifting <a href="Rakhi">Rakhi with Puja</a> Thali and treasure the day for lifetime.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">Personalized Gift Items</span></strong><br /> <span style="font-size: 13px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">Gift Jaipur provides a variety of personalised gifts which can directly touch the heart of your brother/sister. Personalized gift includes photo of your brother/sister on a <a href="Mugs">mug</a> and many more innovative ideas which make the festival more special and pleasant for all brothers and sisters</span></p>', '', 1, 9, 0, 36, '2012-07-14 18:24:48', 62, '', '2012-07-14 19:04:22', 62, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2012-07-14 18:24:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', 'show_title=\nlink_titles=\nshow_intro=\nshow_section=\nlink_section=\nshow_category=\nlink_category=\nshow_vote=\nshow_author=\nshow_create_date=\nshow_modify_date=\nshow_pdf_icon=\nshow_print_icon=\nshow_email_icon=\nlanguage=\nkeyref=\nreadmore=', 6, 0, 2, '', '', 0, 3, 'html_title=\nmeta_description=\nmeta_keywords=\nrobots=index, follow\ngooglebot=\ncopyright='),
(61, 'Send Love to your loved ones in the form of Gifts ', 'Send-Love-to-your-loved-ones-in-the-form-of-Gifts', '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6.0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: Helvetica; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; color: #262626; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 217; background: white;">New way of sending gifts</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 6.0pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica CE&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; color: #262626; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 217; background: white;">Do you want to send gifts to your relatives? Are you searching for a reliable and affordable partner who can help deliver your gifts to your friends and family without any issues? Are you one of those who like to compare prices before deciding to make a purchase? Are you caught up in your office schedule that you cannot find the time to choose a gift for your wife on her birthday? If your answer to all these questions is a yes then you need to head towards the online gift shops rather than mull over how to convince your loved ones that you did not get the spare time to go hunting for their gift.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top: 0in; margin-right: -4.5pt; margin-bottom: 6.0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica CE&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; color: #262626; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 217; background: white;">There are various national and </span><span style="font-size: 10.0pt; font-family: &quot;Helvetica CE&quot;; color: #262626; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 217;"><a href="http://www.giftjaipur.com/"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma; color: #262626; mso-themecolor: text1; mso-themetint: 217; background: white;">local gift s