(3, 5, 0, 'Anukriti Saxena', '', '', '"Thanks a ton for creating the wedding anniversary of my sister even more spectacular with the fabulous flower bouquet and fresh Cake."', '2012-05-27 01:05:53', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(6, 5, 0, 'Ankur Gupta', 'ankurgupta3453@gmail.com', '', 'Thank you from the core of my heart for sending the superb flower bouquet to my younger brother.', '2012-05-03 11:29:31', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(7, 5, 0, 'Jeenal Sethiya', 'jeenal@gmail.com', '', 'Many Thanks!!! It has always \r\nbeen a pleasure to have placed order with Giftjaipur.com. Appreciate your quick responses and customer service.', '2012-06-20 11:32:06', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(5, 5, 0, 'Nobal Kaushik', 'connectdudi@gmail.com', '', 'Thank you for sending exotic gifts and magnificent flowers to Jaipur on the event of Father''s Day.', '2012-05-17 11:20:52', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(8, 5, 0, 'Prateek Pundhir', 'pprateekpundhir@gmail.com', '', 'Excellent service. Thanx a lot..really appreciate the gift and the service provided...keep up the good work!!!', '2012-07-01 21:18:14', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(9, 5, 0, 'Ravina Verma', '', '', 'I  ordered for Rakhi, got a best buy and a  fine  response.', '2012-07-14 08:51:30', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(10, 5, 0, 'Ruhi Saxena', 'ruhi.saxena2011@gmail.com', '', 'I am pretty much happy with giftjaipur service....Customization of the gift is the best facility one could ever have to make our dear ones more special because it seems more personal...I got fresh flowers bouquet & yummy designer cake even at midnight(It was the same as it was mailed + Delicious)...Add-ons Balloons and candles added flavour to my surprise for my hubby''s 1st bdy after our marriage.Thank you Naman.... Good job..Looking forward to take your services again :)\n5 Star ***** overall Ratings(Presentation+Service(customization + Delivery)+Taste)', '2012-07-15 13:11:32', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(11, 5, 0, 'Punya Pathak', 'punya.pathak@gmail.com', '', 'GiftJaipur is an excellent service which I used to send fresh flowers & Delicious Cake to my fiancee. Flowers (Red Roses)were really fresh, she said they were like Velvet!!! Cake was prepared in Morning and very fresh, overall presentation was good, delivery was on time. Overall it''s an excellent service. I will use it again and I recommend others to use their services. 5* rating. Thanks a lot for providing such an excellent services.', '2012-07-18 07:19:36', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(12, 5, 0, 'upbgza', 'xmoucb@hvftjj.com', '', 'QvvsXk  zjlowxwgxhpm, [url=http://mazcgreusxze.com/]mazcgreusxze[/url], [link=http://dxmezxvnuxgo.com/]dxmezxvnuxgo[/link], http://ezianotolaoi.com/', '2012-07-19 02:59:59', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(13, 5, 0, 'Jitender Meena', 'jk_iitk@yahoo.com', '', 'It was my first time using this website for sending online gift. I am extremely happy with the service and speed i got. I recommend GiftJaipur to all other especially young generation.\n\nGood Luck GiftJaipur Team\n\nJitender\nSeoul, S.Korea', '2012-07-21 06:28:01', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(14, 5, 0, 'Bayi', 'luwille@yahoo.de', '', 'For my granny''s 80th bidthray, I searched for an old friend that she used to play music with and asked him to perform a few songs with her at her party. If you could take her to a place where she used to go when she was younger or take her to see a band that she used to like years ago it''s a really nice treat. Nostalgia is a great gift.', '2012-07-22 03:19:58', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(15, 5, 0, 'cwtuhgyyg', 'axwuqm@qgtlmx.com', '', 'Pvb3ZT  epuqnlrdsrdd, [url=http://fvpdvdlciuic.com/]fvpdvdlciuic[/url], [link=http://xtqzjulskfkf.com/]xtqzjulskfkf[/link], http://vbhplaxxjwdd.com/', '2012-07-24 04:54:03', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(16, 5, 0, 'Guest', 'monika.yadav997@gmail.com', '', 'It was a great experience placing order by this site. Service they provide is very fast and reliable. I am really very satisfied with the response I received.\r\n\r\nI highly recommend people of our city to use its service.\r\n\r\nBEST WISHES !!!\r\n\r\nMonika Yadav\r\nPune.', '2012-07-29 09:57:37', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(17, 5, 0, 'Guest', 'rel223@llsdk.com', '', 'vbvc', '2012-07-30 04:20:57', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(18, 5, 0, 'Guest', 'superidea120@gmail.com', '', 'Great website guys and all the very best. May god bless you with all the success. \nFew suggestion that I observed while surfing the website, though I never used the service ;) :\n\n> Testimonials seems to be faked...As a customer I would also like to read not so good or atleast neutral experiences....seeing all cloud 9 testimonial suggests something fishy with the service.\n\n> Fonts and colors are much more brighter that the size of the content....may be we want to see many more option in the service to match the look and feel of the design :)\n\n> No matter, how many times I refresh, it takes the same amount to load which is annoying...we want to see better caching in views for easy and fast surfing \n\n> Few of the text(Especially when registering) not proper....customers hate to see the text being cut...example is Indian Ruppe in Change currency\n\n> Would be nice to see review of other customer about the product or atleast some stars...so that we know which is good and which is not so nice...\n\n\nI observed above points while surfing for few minutes and though of putting it here so that it could be thought about by the jaipurgift team and by no chance mean to demotivate the team. Again Good Work and keep it up :)', '2012-07-30 04:42:37', 0, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(19, 5, 0, 'Praveen', 'praveendani74@gmail.com', '', 'Very reliable service.. you made our day!! Very prompt and fresh delivery. \nMany thanks and keep it up with great service. \n\nWITH BEST WISHES!!\n\nPraveen Dani', '2012-08-04 11:27:58', 1, 0, 'a:0:{}'),
(20, 5, 0, 'Amrita pritam', '', '', 'It was a gr8 n nice experience with this team. i never ever saw this kind of fast service. You guys are doing a very gr8 job. keep it up.\n\nGOOD Luck!!\n:)', '2012-08-05 12:46:57', 1, 148, 'a:0:{}');
