(271, 1, 0, 'jm02', 'The famous MAAKHAN CHOR in a dazzling yellow satin dress.', '<p>The famous MAAKHAN CHOR in a dazzling yellow satin dress is just looking so authentic and traditional and is waiting for you to swing him in the cradle and to pamper him as Janmashtami is his birthday. So celebrate the festival in style and let your home dazzle. This cute little deity of bal gopal is 2 inches in size and he is just worth watching because of its dynamic look. The deity of bal gopal is made of made of brass. His beautiful jewelry is made of metal and is decked with meenakari work, American Diamonds and with shimmering stones. The beautiful crown of bal gopal is also decked with marvelous ‘motis’ and also there is a ‘MORE PANKHI embellished with ZARI’ which is attached to the crown to give a more authentic and artistic look. This shown Bal Gopal is also wearing a PAIR OF EARRINGS and TILAK which is authentically designed with American Diamonds and a ravishing red color stones in its center. This cute little bal gopal is also holding a metal baansuri (flute) which is also adorned with American Diamonds and meenakari work.</p>', 'resized/2_inches_Bal_Gop_50215c140cdae_100x100.jpg', '2_inches_Bal_Gop_50215c1423435.jpg', 'Y', 0.0000, 'pounds', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 'inches', '', 0, 1344297600, '', 'N', 0, NULL, 1344363540, 1344397149, '2 inches Bal Gopal in Yellow Satin Dress', 0, '', '', 0, 'piece', 0, 'N,N,N,N,N,N,20%,10%,', 'none,0,0,1', '', '0,0'),
(270, 1, 0, 'jm1', 'This set of beautiful jewellery is made all in metal and is decked with Meenakari Work, Diamonds, Shimmering Stones, Zari work and Beads (motis) on the Crown.', '<p>This set of beautiful jewellery is made all in metal and is decked with Meenakari Work, Diamonds, Shimmering Stones, Zari work and Beads (motis) on the Crown.</p>\r\n</br><p><h5>This set of SHRINGAR includes-</h5></p>\r\n</br><p>Mukut</p>\r\n</br><p>Morpankhi</p>\r\n</br><p>Tilak</p>\r\n</br><p>\r\nEarrings</p>\r\n</br><p>Necklace</p>\r\n</br><p>Baansuri</p>\r\n</br><p>Baal</p>', 'resized/3_inches_Krishna_50215a699342a_100x100.jpg', '3_inches_Krishna_50215a6997f61.jpg', 'Y', 0.0000, 'pounds', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 'inches', '', 0, 1344297600, '', 'N', 0, NULL, 1344363113, 1344397199, '3 inches Krishnaji Shringar with Zari Mukut', 0, '', '', 0, 'piece', 0, 'N,N,N,N,N,N,20%,10%,', 'none,0,0,1', '', '0,0'),
(273, 1, 0, 'jm04', 'Mawa Kesar Peda made of Milk, Sugar and Dryfruits', '<p>Mawa Kesar Peda made of Milk, Sugar and Dryfruits.</p>\r\n<p>Special Peda from “Kanha”, The famous sweet shop of Jaipur. Delivered by GiftJaipur.</p>', 'resized/Mawa_Peda__kesar_50227c1c5b23b_100x100.jpg', 'Mawa_Peda__kesar_50227c1c63793.jpg', 'Y', 1.0000, 'Kg', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 'inches', '', 0, 1344384000, '', 'N', 0, NULL, 1344437276, 1344437483, 'Mawa Peda (kesar)', 0, '', '', 0, 'piece', 0, 'N,N,N,N,N,N,20%,10%,', 'none,0,0,1', '', '0,0'),
(272, 1, 0, 'jm03', 'Sweets are one of the most favoured gift during Janmashtami. Lord Krishna was very fond of milk and sweets made of milk, since then sweets have been a popular choice for gifting purpose.', '<p>Sweets are one of the most favoured gift during Janmashtami. Lord Krishna was very fond of milk and sweets made of milk, since then sweets have been a popular choice for gifting purpose. </p>\r\n</br><p>Sweets  are made by ''Kanha'' famous  sweet  shop  of  Jaipur.</p>', 'resized/Milk_Sweet_50215cd0b29db_100x100.jpg', 'Milk_Sweet_50215cd0b4c42.jpg', 'Y', 1.0000, 'Kg', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 'inches', '', 0, 1344297600, '', 'N', 0, NULL, 1344363728, 1344363728, 'Milk Sweet', 0, '', '', 0, 'piece', 0, 'N,N,N,N,N,N,20%,10%,', 'none,0,0,1', '', '0,0'),
(274, 1, 0, 'jm05', 'Marvelously carved Radha- Krishna on the white metal wall hanging depict the religious bend that persists in you and has been bestowed by the Indian culture.', '<p>Marvelously carved Radha- Krishna on the white metal wall hanging depict the religious bend that persists in you and has been bestowed by the Indian culture. Designed perfectly to enhance the blissful charm of the dwelling, brighten and invigorate your home with this splendid decorative.</p>', 'resized/Prem_Pratima__Wh_50227ef585807_100x100.jpg', 'Prem_Pratima__Wh_50227ef5b9b65.jpg', 'Y', 0.0000, 'pounds', 0.0000, 0.0000, 0.0000, 'inches', '', 0, 1344384000, '', 'N', 0, NULL, 1344438005, 1344438005, 'Prem Pratima: White Metal Sculpture', 0, '', '', 0, 'piece', 65537, 'N,N,N,N,N,N,20%,10%,', 'none,0,0,1', '', '0,0'),
